<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
  <title>Zona 44</title>
  <%= csrf_meta_tags %>
  <%= csp_meta_tag %>

  <style>
    @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@600&display=swap');

    :root {
      --color-bg: #ffffff;
      --color-primary: #111827;
      --color-secondary: #6b7280;
      --color-accent: #374151;
      --color-button-bg: #111827;
      --color-button-text: #ffffff;
      --radius: 0.75rem;
      --transition: 0.3s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
      --max-width: 1200px;
      --shadow-light: 0 4px 8px rgb(0 0 0 / 0.05);
      --shadow-hover: 0 8px 16px rgb(0 0 0 / 0.10);
    }

    *, *::before, *::after {
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    body {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
      background-color: var(--color-bg);
      color: var(--color-secondary);
      font-size: 18px;
      line-height: 1.5;
      -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
      -moz-osx-font-smoothing: grayscale;
    }

    a {
      color: inherit;
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    /* Sticky header */
    header {
      position: sticky;
      top: 0;
      background: var(--color-bg);
      border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
      box-shadow: var(--shadow-light);
      z-index: 100;
      padding: 1rem 2rem;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      max-width: var(--max-width);
      margin: 0 auto;
    }
    
    /* Logo */
    .logo {
      height: 48px;
      width: auto;
      cursor: default;
      user-select: none;
    }

    /* Icon container */
    .iconos {
      display: flex;
      gap: 1.5rem;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .icono {
      width: 28px;
      height: 28px;
      filter: grayscale(100%);
      transition: filter var(--transition);
      cursor: pointer;
    }

    .icono:hover,
    .icono:focus {
      filter: grayscale(0);
      outline: none;
    }

    /* Main container */
    .container {
      max-width: var(--max-width);
      margin: 3rem auto 6rem;
      padding: 0 2rem;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 3rem;
    }

    /* Principal section styling */
    .principal {
      background: #f9fafb;
      border-radius: var(--radius);
      box-shadow: var(--shadow-light);
      padding: 3rem 2.5rem;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 3rem;
      text-align: center;
      transition: box-shadow var(--transition);
      user-select: none;
    }
    .principal:hover,
    .principal:focus-within {
      box-shadow: var(--shadow-hover);
    }

    /* Data text container */
    .datos {
      max-width: 520px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      color: var(--color-primary);
    }

    .datos h2 {
      font-size: 48px;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
      color: var(--color-primary);
    }

    .datos p {
      font-size: 18px;
      margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
      color: var(--color-secondary);
    }

    /* dato2 container for sub-text */
    .dato2 {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 2.5rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      font-size: 18px;
      color: var(--color-primary);
    }

    /* Buttons container */
    .butones {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 2rem;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }

    .boton {
      background-color: var(--color-button-bg);
      color: var(--color-button-text);
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 18px;
      padding: 0.85rem 2.25rem;
      border-radius: var(--radius);
      border: none;
      cursor: pointer;
      box-shadow: var(--shadow-light);
      transition:
        background-color var(--transition),
        transform var(--transition),
        box-shadow var(--transition);
      user-select: none;
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    .boton:hover,
    .boton:focus {
      background-color: #000000;
      box-shadow: var(--shadow-hover);
      transform: scale(1.05);
      outline: none;
    }

    /* Footer styling */
    footer {
      max-width: var(--max-width);
      margin: 4rem auto 3rem;
      padding: 0 2rem;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 2rem;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      color: var(--color-secondary);
      font-weight: 600;
      user-select: none;
    }

    .boton2 {
      background: transparent;
      color: var(--color-accent);
      font-weight: 600;
      border: 2px solid transparent;
      padding: 0.5rem 1.25rem;
      border-radius: var(--radius);
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: all var(--transition);
      text-decoration: none;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      user-select: none;
    }

    .boton2:hover,
    .boton2:focus {
      color: #000;
      border-color: #000;
      outline: none;
      transform: scale(1.05);
    }

    /* Footer paragraph styled like a button but not clickable */
    footer p.boton2 {
      cursor: default;
      user-select: text;
      background: transparent;
      border: none;
      color: var(--color-secondary);
      font-weight: 500;
      font-size: 16px;
    }

  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <header>
      <%= image_tag("logo.jpg", alt: "Logo del negocio", class: "logo") %>
      <div class="iconos">
        <a href="https://wa.me/3116306019?text=Hola%2C%20estoy%20interesado%20en%20sus%20productos" target="_blank" aria-label="Whatsapp">
          <%= image_tag('iconos/whatsapp.png', alt: "WhatsApp", class: "icono") %>
        </a>
        <a href="https://www.instagram.com/zona44gastrobar" target="_blank" aria-label="Instagram">
          <%= image_tag('iconos/instagram.png', alt: "Instagram", class: "icono") %>
        </a>
      </div>
    </header>

    <section class="principal" role="main" aria-label="Bienvenida a Zona 44">
      <div class="datos">
        <h2>😊 Bienvenid@s</h2>
        <p>Zona 44 es un lugar en el cual vas a disfrutar y pasar ratos agradables.</p>
        <div class="dato2" aria-label="Opciones del servicio">
          <p>Domicilios</p>
          <p>Para llevar</p> 
          <p>En el local</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="butones" role="navigation" aria-label="Enlaces principales">
        <a href="https://maps.app.goo.gl/CdUGHEEFwdie5cvV9" target="_blank" class="boton" rel="noopener noreferrer">Cómo llegar</a>  
        <%= link_to "Ver Menú📝", menu_path, class: "boton" %>
        <a href="https://wa.me/3116306019?text=Hola%2C%20estoy%20interesado%20en%20sus%20productos" target="_blank" class="boton" rel="noopener noreferrer" aria-label="Contacto por WhatsApp">WhatsApp</a>
      </div> 
    </section>
  </div> 

  <footer>
    <%= link_to "Menú digital", menu_path, class: "boton2" %>
     <%= link_to 'Iniciar sesión', new_user_session_path, style: "color: red; margin-left: 20px;", class: "boton2" %>
    <p class="boton2">Reportar algo</p>
  </footer>
</body>
</html>
